{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4b3d1ad7-68e1-4807-9b41-8e5c2fff9f8a","content":"You're on **MSTest 3.8.2** / .NET 9. Here's the modern recommended pattern:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests\n{\n    private readonly TestContext _testContext;\n\n    // Constructor injection for TestContext (MSTest v3+)\n    public MyTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        _testContext = testContext;\n        // Synchronous init logic here\n    }\n\n    // Async per-test initialization\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task SetupAsync()\n    {\n        // Async init (e.g., seed a database, start a service)\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void ExampleTest()\n    {\n        _testContext.WriteLine(\"Running test...\");\n        Assert.IsTrue(true);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- **Constructor injection** of `TestContext` is the modern MSTest v3 approach — no need for a settable property.\n- Use the **constructor** for synchronous setup.\n- Use **`[TestInitialize] async Task`** for async setup (supported since MSTest v3).\n- `[ClassInitialize]` also supports `async Task` if you need one-time async class-level setup.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"54d49c91-5d7e-41a5-9740-03329fbe4aaf","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"They're using MSTest 3.8.2 on .NET 9.0. Let me provide the recommended modern MSTest approach.\n\nIn MSTest v3, the recommended pattern is:\n1. `TestContext` is injected via constructor (no more static property for class-level context or instance property)\n2. `ClassInitialize` and `ClassCleanup` are static methods with `[ClassInitialize]` and `[ClassCleanup]` attributes\n3. `TestInitialize` and `TestCleanup` are instance methods\n4. For async initialization, you can use `async Task` return types on `TestInitialize`/`TestCleanup` methods\n\n\n5. `[ClassInitialize]` also supports `async Task` for class-level setup\n\nLet me put together a clear example showing the modern approach.","outputTokens":564,"requestId":"1BC8:49329:4FC5FF:5AD052:6A03D72D"},"id":"6f0b22f2-7f55-496b-b1bf-2a0b2c1d46b5","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:43:22.548Z","parentId":"c9dd726f-e931-4d32-bc63-33eff194a664"}
